HEADWORD: Argillite
<hw>Ar"gil*lite</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ clay +
<ets>-lite</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Min.)</fld> <def>Argillaceous schist or
slate; clay slate. Its colors is bluish or blackish gray, sometimes
greenish gray, brownish red, etc.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Ar`gil*lit"ic</wf>, <pos>a.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
